<H1>Examples of setting vi options temporarily</H1>

<P>To set the wrapmargin:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>:set wm=5</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This sets the wrapmargin to five characters. In insert
mode, text will automatically wrap to a new line when the
cursor is five characters from the right edge of the
screen.</P>

<HR>

<P>To display line numbers:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>:set number</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This causes <STRONG>vi</STRONG> to display a line number (starting at 1)
at the start of every 
<A HREF="../didyou/vi.1.html">line of text</A>.</P>

